data.description: Seller is willing to contribute up to $5,000 in Flex Money for rate buy down or closing costs for the buyer! Beautiful Craftsman style cottage, located in the community of Sonoma Ridge. Come see what sets this home apart from others. Open floor plan design and large island and pantry in the kitchen, double car garage, and covered back porch. This open floor plan has 9' ceilings throughout with tray ceilings finished in crown molding and ceiling fans in the great room and master bedroom. Other features include: granite countertops, Samsung stainless steel appliances, beautiful wood cabinetry, large laundry room convenient from the garage, and luxury vinyl plank flooring in all areas except bedrooms. Master bath has garden tub, separate shower, double vanity, water closet, and a spacious walk-in closet. The Sonoma Ridge community features low-maintenance, four-side brick, cozy cottage homes with modern amenities, surrounded by nature, close to major employment centers like Navy Federal, and minutes from the interstate.
